div.p:
If now it shall please God to Humble me into the Lowest of a Sackcloth Condition, and to enable me with his Grace, I shall not Refuse the Life of Mephibosheth, during Davids Absence from Jerusalem upon the Conspiracy of Absalom, and Achitophel, till his Return; which was a Figure of the Antichristian
Sam. 19. 24. Ʋndermine of the Kingdom of Christ that hath so long been, and that still continues;
And I shall Humbly wait for a Restoration of my state, and an Ability for Righteousness, in the nearer Approaches of the Return of Christ in his Kingdom of Glory; when what He hath enabled me to write for it, shall be Recall'd, as the Act of Mordecai toward that Great Prince Ahasuerus; when that Est. 6. 1. Greater, then He, shall please to Remember me for Good, and to spare me in the Multitude of his Mercies, Nehem. 13. 22. Or that sooner dying, as I have most Reason to expect; He will in Infinite Grace, and Pardon Receive me as the Thief on the Cross into Paradise with Himself; and Remember me, when Luke 23. 42. He Comes in (not into) His Kingdom.

The latter Oath in this Prophecy, in full Agreement with the former requires, there should be no more Time, Times, nor Half Time, which the former Oath Allowed; But that at the Seventh Angel Beginning, (as we well translate 
                  〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
               ) to sound, and all the while, He is sounding, the Mystery should be in Finishing, till Finish'd in the Kingdom in Glory.
